<section id='ColormapFocus'>
<title>ColormapFocus</title>

<cmdsynopsis>
  <command>ColormapFocus</command>
	<group choice='plain'>
		<arg choice='plain'>FollowsMouse</arg>
    <arg choice='plain'>FollowsFocus</arg>
	</group>
</cmdsynopsis>

<para>By default, fvwm installs the colormap of the window that the
cursor is in.  If you use</para>

<programlisting>
ColormapFocus <fvwmopt cmd="ColormapFocus" opt="FollowsFocus"/>
</programlisting>

<para>then the installed colormap is the one for the window that
currently has the keyboard focus.</para>

</section>
